    <div class="lx-tcard__body">
      <div class="lx-tcard__role">C.E.O. · Founder</div>
      <div class="lx-tcard__name">Michael Close</div>
      <div class="lx-tcard__bio">
        <p>Since founding LogixX Pharma in 2010, Michael has focused on leveraging the uniqueness of the company with an emphasis on strong execution and the highest ethical and regulatory standards — primarily in the metabolic, paediatric, and fertility markets.</p>
        <p>Overseeing licensing, partnerships and new project initiation, Michael has a vision to support patient communities and healthcare professionals through innovation, lifecycle management and geographical expansion.</p>
        <p>Michael is the MHRA approved Responsible Person of LogixX Pharma Ltd, and serves as Chairman of CytoSwim Limited and Shard Speciality Pharma Ltd. Prior to LogixX Pharma he held senior posts at Merck Serono, Solvay and Bayer. He holds a degree in Biomedical Science from the University of Wolverhampton.</p>
