    <div class="lx-tcard__body">
      <div class="lx-tcard__role">Chief Scientific Officer</div>
      <div class="lx-tcard__name">Professor Ralf Henkel</div>
      <div class="lx-tcard__bio">
        <p>Professor Henkel joined LogixX Pharma as Chief Scientific Officer in July 2020 following an esteemed career in academic science. He studied Biology and Chemistry in Marburg, Germany.</p>
        <p>From January 2014 to May 2020, he was Head of Department of Medical Bioscience at the University of the Western Cape, South Africa, where he is now an Extraordinary Professor.</p>
        <p>Professor Henkel is Editor-in-Chief of ANDROLOGIA. He has supervised 71 graduating students, published 167 research papers and review articles, 47 book chapters and 2 books. His h-index is 41.</p>
